================================================================================
License compatibility
================================================================================

The MIT-licensed `arduinojson` is compatible with both Apache-2.0 and
AGPL-3.0-or-later. The Apache-2.0 components (`zap_common`,
`metrics`) are compatible with the AGPL-3.0-or-later ones in a
combined firmware build: the combined work is distributed under
AGPL-3.0-or-later; each upstream component retains its own license
when used in isolation.
